snippet.title: Let's play MCGG together! | Soft Launch Video | Magic Chess: Go Go
snippet.description:
MCGG is an MLBB Multiplayer Strategy Game, where fun & strategy are in your hands! Get amazing free rewards including 12 FREE Commanders, Chessboard, Commander skins, Avatar Borders and more. See you in MCGG!
Soft Launch in MY & SG Now; Pre-Reg Rewards for Other APAC Regions.
